<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قُلتُ:</span> انظر: <span style="color:#950000">"تراجم رجال الحاكم"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
